description:
Hi new visitor!
Welcome to CCNP ROUTE Labs course! This is a completely theory-free, completely-configuration course.
If you know the theory, nice, check the commands necessary to complete a task. If you don't know the theory, it's OK, you will get enough to get you going and do the job you are assigned.


As a student in my community you will receive early free or highly discounted offers for my future courses (and trust me, you will be surprised what you are going to get!)


I guarantee, by the end of this course you will receive enough information and hand-on experience to fully accomplish a CCNP job role and if you feel you don't, you have one month to claim your money back!
There is a Q&A section in Udemy and I will answer your questions personally and also don't forget to rate me and write reviews.
I also appreciate your messages in that they will let me know what to do to improve my courses.

Please like my facebook page and join my youtube channel and view some free videos and receive promos on my next courses.
title: CCNP ROUTE Labs
